# VEHICLE::SET_VEHICLE_HAS_STRONG_AXLES

## Summary
Sets so that axles dont break easily

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** vehicle
* **BOOL** set

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
if true, axles won't bend.
